{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"8ac30165b9","title":"中央批转刘格平同志关于抓紧春耕工作的意见","origin":"根据中央文件浙江省嵊县军事管制委员会翻印件。原标题：刘格平同志关于抓紧春耕工作的意见。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d8d2a91410","index":0,"year":1967,"month":2,"day":5,"articleId":"8ac30165b9"}],"tags":[{"id":"11ef425d44","name":"刘格平","type":"人物"},{"id":"4206ce6bf3","name":"红卫兵运动","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"7aaf655bdf","name":"山西文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"14b50d0015","type":"title","text":"中央批转刘格平同志关于抓紧春耕工作的意见","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"dece62bd2f","type":"appellation","text":"各中央局，各省、市、自治区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"663d7450e4","type":"paragraph","text":"刘格平同志关于抓紧春耕工作的意见，很好。现发给你们参考。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"b739070d2d","type":"paragraph","text":" 中  央一九六七年二月五日","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"afea719245","type":"paragraph","text":"太原革命造反总部刘格平来电话报告：山西农村情况很乱，回乡青年、地富子弟也组织了红卫兵。农村干部躺下不干等着交班。如不很快采取措施，即将影响春耕春种。我们准备和陈永贵、李顺达一起谈谈农村怎么办，帮助他们整理个材料，准备在《山西日报》上发表或写个社论。《人民日报》是否转登？我们准备提几条：","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"6cb7b8afe6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）依靠贫下中农，团结中农。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"c7194f2275","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）学习毛主席著作，学习语录、社论，干部要担负起来，不能离开岗位，有错误的将功补罪。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"4a6b07561c","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）农村大忙，准备春耕春播，串连学生一定参加劳动，决不能妨碍春季生产。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"6cf718e8cb","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）地、富、反、坏、右如乱说乱动，坚决镇压。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"b894277a8f","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）不管谁妨碍春耕春播要受处分。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"365ac48d5e","type":"paragraph","text":"从现在来看，我们如不赶快表态，农村是不行的。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"},{"id":"b0d63639bb","type":"paragraph","text":"以上打算当否，请指示。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9"}],"page":{"id":"18fbb7b4be","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"8ac30165b9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}